; Prompt the user to run the script - use a Yes/No prompt (4 - see help file)
$answer = MsgBox(4, "AutoIt 例子", "这个脚本将会调用两个自定义函数.  运行?")


; Check the user's answer to the prompt (see the help file for MsgBox return values)
